body:
able to reproduce on windows 11 with just html/css:
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body>
    <style>
      html, div, body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .wrap {
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: #0c0614;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        color: white;
      }
      .wrap > * {
        pointer-events: none;
      }
    </style>
    <div class="wrap" data-tauri-drag-region>
      <h1>drag me</h1>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
```
